        WEB_SITE=https://github.com/ziglang/zig.vim/
         ENTERED=20200817
         UPDATED=20200817
           SHORT="File detection and syntax highlighting for zig"

cat << EOF
File detection and syntax highlighting for the zig programming language.
This plugin enables automatic code formatting on save by default using zig fmt.
To disable it, you can use this configuration in vimrc:
   let g:zig_fmt_autosave = 0
EOF
